# Verify before handoff

Mọi thay đổi code cần kiểm tra trước khi bàn giao.

Follow the project skill `.cursor/skills/verify-before-handoff/SKILL.md`.

Before telling the user work is done:

1. Run typecheck / lint on touched files when applicable
2. After Prisma schema changes: `prisma generate`, `prisma db push`, then **restart `npm run dev`** (PrismaClient is cached on `globalThis` in [src/lib/prisma.ts](src/lib/prisma.ts))
3. Reproduce the changed user flow and check terminal/browser for errors
4. Do not claim bàn giao ready until checks that apply have passed
